data.description: Staycation! Recently renovated and the views are endless. Overlooking the fountain and picturesque scenery in all direction, you may not notice the soaring ceiling with wood lap to the peek! The fireplace is your centerpiece of the home and the open feel allows kitchen, dining, living rooms all surrounding it. The large primary suite was been recently updated and has a beautiful private bathroom while bedrooms two and three share a large bathroom as well. The hardwood floors are throughout the entire living and sleeping areas with tile in the bathrooms. There is a large back deck that allow a relaxing backdrop to those views!
